cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is about improving image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed framework also involves reinforcement learning (cs.LG) and autoencoding (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of different input features such as detected objects and scene graph features suggests that multimedia (cs.MM) could also be a relevant sub-category.
